Class AreaSummaryDataNew

  • java.lang.Object
    • simpplle.comcode.AreaSummaryDataNew

  • public class AreaSummaryDataNew
extends java.lang.Object
    The University of Montana owns copyright of the designated documentation contained within this file as part of the software product designated by Uniform Resource Identifier UM-OpenSIMPPLLE-1.0.     This is the new area summary data class which replaces the old Area SummaryData class deprecated in V2.5 This class contains getters and setters for

  • season
  • acres
  • unit id
  • process
  • group
  • ownership
  • rational probablility
Since:
V2.5
